p: Eugenol-TyrRS (1JIJ) interactions: The second major compound eugenol (6.3 kcal/mol) was bounded only by hydrophobic interactions to Tyr36, Asp177, Gly72, Asn124, Thr75, Tyr170, Asp40, Gln174, Ile200, Gln196, Gly192, Val191, Gln190, Gly38 (van der Waals interactions) and to Cys37 (4.39) and Leu70 (4.84) (Alkyl/Pi-Alkyl).
